  "instructions": [
    "In a medium bowl, whip the egg whites until stiff peaks form.",
    "Add the granulated sugar and whip until stiff and glossy.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the double cream, smoked sea salt, vanilla extract, smoked coffee, and lemon zest.",
    "In a separate bowl, whip the egg whites and sugar until stiff and glossy.",
    "Fold the egg whites into the cream mixture until no white streaks remain.",
    "Pour the mixture into 4 individual serving cups.",
    "Refrigerate for at least 2 hours.",
    "Before serving, sprinkle with smoked sea salt and a drizzle of lemon juice."
